parameters: Elmgar actually has a map now! However, there’s not much going on with it at the moment, so you can still use this hub area to travel to any of the interesting locations in town. The one exception is travelling to Skirts and More, check the northern sign to figure out how to do that if you want to see the events for travelling there. Also, the only way to reach the guild at the moment is to use the hub area right now.
Also, you can change text and battle animation speeds in the menu, if you want things faster or slower than the default.
The game now has a paperdoll system for the character! By default it will appear during check appearance, but you can also set it to remain on the screen through the key item "misc settings."

I'm also implementing an alternate way to display text. This will essentially combine multiple text boxes into one larger one. When this happens, character text will have quotation marks surrounding them, and will be in color, to indicate who is speaking.

\c[4]"This would be you, the player, speaking. The player's text will always be in this color."
